        "TileImage": "$($repository 7809503d-5324-4e73-8915-db8b1e029151).Image",
        "Description": "A rogue cell has infiltrated this year&apos;s IAGO auction, attemting to sell compromised ICA intelligence. While the main targets remain out of reach, these operatives threaten the stability of the operation. Eliminate all involved silently to maintain normalcy and ensure next years auction proceeds without disruption.\r\rEric Hubert &quot;The Broker&quot;\rHailey Brennan &quot;The Architect\rRoger DuPont &quot;The Gatekeeper&quot;\rPhilippe Dutrieux &quot;The Stagehand&quot;\rGuillaume Garceau &quot;The Watchman&quot;\r\r47 Remeber &quot;Unseen, Unheard&quot;",
